    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a miner traveling from asteroid to asteroid collecting valuable minerals and lost technology. Improve your spacecraft and survive attacks from an unknown menace that threatens all existence.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COLLECT MINERALS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel to different asteroids to collect resources and lost technology.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >     <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113690/extras/eb56692b18fe424839603812bec8fa27.poster.avif?t=1765030788\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113690/extras/eb56692b18fe424839603812bec8fa27.webm?t=1765030788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >IMPROVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the collected minerals to upgrade your ship with found technology, from triple mining rays to photon thrusters. Build space stations and drones to help with your task.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                         <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113690/extras/35997637667a1c20af2007c40dd4d2a7.poster.avif?t=1765030788\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113690/extras/35997637667a1c20af2007c40dd4d2a7.webm?t=1765030788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <br>SURVIVE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Galaxy is in extreme danger, and so are you. Survive unknown threats from beyond The Anomaly. Upgrade your equipment and use your skills to complete The Mission.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113690/extras/deae1cbcb4e8883055686abe3425d01f.poster.avif?t=1765030788\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3113690/extras/deae1cbcb4e8883055686abe3425d01f.webm?t=1765030788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You are the last hope. </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
